Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.67,0:01:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類因人口膨脹而向宇宙移民已過了半個世紀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.26,0:01:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球周圍漂浮著巨大的人工都市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.71,0:01:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為人類的「第二故鄉」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.37,0:01:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人們就在這裏出生、成長、生兒育女\N並走向死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.59,0:02:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙世紀0079年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.71,0:02:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離地球最遠的宇宙都市SIDE 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.31,0:02:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以ZION公國之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.57,0:02:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向地球聯邦政府發起了獨立戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.13,0:02:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在開始一個月的戰鬥里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.35,0:02:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION公國和地球聯邦軍有半數以上的人口死去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.23,0:02:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人們對於自己的行為產生了恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.58,0:02:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,『卡爾瑪之死』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.79,0:03:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問你父親打算何時會到地球呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.52,0:03:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒聽他說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.43,0:03:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若他來的話,可以介紹我認識嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.14,0:03:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起！我先失陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.48,0:03:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀！卡爾瑪上校真英俊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.75,0:03:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.71,0:03:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他很英俊啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.35,0:03:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最討厭便是這類人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.49,0:03:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若他們知道有White Base這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.59,0:03:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能會嚇一跳！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.83,0:03:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我們要加強監視，我要奪取那艘聯邦軍艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.36,0:03:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡爾瑪，那邊的紳士是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.97,0:03:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有用得上我的話隨便說吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.77,0:03:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是前市長 艾森威
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.84,0:03:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他很憎恨ZION國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.64,0:03:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但為了保護市民，所以留在此地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.68,0:03:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來他很頑固呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.21,0:03:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾森威先生的千金依榭蓮娜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.69,0:04:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我失陪一會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.87,0:04:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在最前線仍要說戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.81,0:04:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡爾瑪真是大少爺脾氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.91,0:04:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION國最高統帥的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.75,0:04:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你爸爸是否不願意將妳嫁給他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.15,0:04:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.55,0:04:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也猜到你爸爸會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.42,0:04:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對我來說，ZION和聯邦也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.79,0:04:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡爾瑪就是卡爾瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.99,0:04:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就只愛你一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.30,0:04:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依榭蓮娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.00,0:04:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我寧可離開爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.53,0:04:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也要和你一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.87,0:04:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我卻不可背叛我爸爸和ZION國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.81,0:04:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.81,0:04:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在有個可取得聯邦軍機密的大好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.14,0:04:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果成功的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.94,0:05:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父親也會答應我的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.55,0:05:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡爾瑪少爺...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.42,0:05:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果到時爸爸還不允許
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.94,0:05:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就要離開ZION
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.36,0:05:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡爾瑪少爺...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.87,0:05:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡爾瑪上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.82,0:05:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.90,0:05:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.91,0:05:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊，說吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.01,0:05:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那艘木馬已進入S.3地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.37,0:05:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.06,0:05:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果給他闖過了這條防線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.71,0:05:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木馬就會進入聯邦軍的範圍了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.65,0:05:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸好我已早有準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.31,0:05:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待會將特別機動隊調去那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.60,0:05:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並通知夏亞少校準備出戰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.12,0:05:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡爾瑪少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.96,0:05:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待我奪取到聯邦的新武器後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.39,0:05:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會送它回國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.16,0:05:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時妳和我一起去好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.71,0:06:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照看ZION軍不會讓我們離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.51,0:06:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以...我們怎辦好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.95,0:06:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長，不如由我用調虎離山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.94,0:06:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引他們到別處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.52,0:06:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，這是沒用的，而且已太遲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.16,0:06:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收到雷達訊息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.99,0:06:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有大批戰機正從北面過來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.83,0:06:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有戰鬥空母吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.17,0:07:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎只有一架！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.30,0:07:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有戰機嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.20,0:07:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來調虎離山計更有必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.03,0:07:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,？？作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.47,0:07:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時White Base就可以走到海面那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.54,0:07:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！想調虎離山或想強行突破也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.66,0:07:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是...是照明彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.41,0:07:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前面是不是烏天尼亞球場？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.98,0:07:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯！是一個球場！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.48,0:07:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好極！將母艦收藏到裏面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.99,0:07:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該夠進入的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.35,0:07:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.68,0:07:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡量防止敵軍發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.18,0:07:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先將所有引擎的熱源關掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.12,0:07:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後趁敵軍不察覺就盡快衝出重圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.52,0:07:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長，我反對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.72,0:07:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.66,0:08:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，你去GUNDAM裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.16,0:08:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱去鋼加農
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.33,0:08:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良、隼人就到鋼坦克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.53,0:08:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別忘了母艦內仍有大量平民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.33,0:08:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實...我也只是平民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.80,0:08:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其它人到戰鬥崗位侯命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等候我的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.51,0:08:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別發出任何聲音，知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.31,0:08:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位聽著，別離開自己房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.26,0:08:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,180度轉向！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.46,0:08:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！180度轉向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.96,0:09:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無路可逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.63,0:09:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒法子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.00,0:09:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正要死...我要落地面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.87,0:09:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對，逃入市區便成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.13,0:09:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，別灰心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.67,0:09:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要大家一起同心協力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.44,0:09:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定會沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.86,0:09:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.88,0:09:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別哭...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.98,0:09:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是你不好，嚇壞他了..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.35,0:09:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底你們在幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.35,0:09:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來，讓我來抱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.49,0:09:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乖...別吵...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.16,0:09:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,BB...BB啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.03,0:09:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，我剛背過身就看不到他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.40,0:09:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,BB，你沒事就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.77,0:09:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到現在仍未有線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.01,0:09:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,未找到那艘木馬戰艦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.71,0:10:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們仍未離開的，繼續找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.25,0:10:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果想令躲起來的傢伙走出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.15,0:10:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最好就是採用密集了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.79,0:10:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！叫他們向地面進行密集轟炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.52,0:10:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別怕...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.79,0:10:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣也炸不中的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.02,0:10:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,值得慶祝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.02,0:11:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來人啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.42,0:11:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐要出去了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.79,0:11:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.74,0:11:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是不會明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.53,0:11:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐，妳現在出去便會白白送死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.36,0:11:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐，別這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.84,0:11:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳父親快來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.70,0:11:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們怎可這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.74,0:11:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.70,0:11:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有地方要去，放開我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.41,0:11:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開我 放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.98,0:11:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和爸爸已經無話可說了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.35,0:11:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說ZION國王兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.37,0:11:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想娶你做皇妃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.38,0:11:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別以為你是我爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.73,0:11:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便可干涉我的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.09,0:11:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有權選擇自己喜歡的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.56,0:11:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不准許
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.46,0:11:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.47,0:12:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,噴射機的鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.61,0:12:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對不可交給小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.13,0:12:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！\N知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.14,0:12:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡爾瑪少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.90,0:12:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣，木馬出來了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.03,0:12:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，暫時未有發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.70,0:12:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底在那裏？為何發現不到？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.17,0:12:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照形勢來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.21,0:12:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那班人已經愈來愈懂得怎樣交戰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.88,0:12:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我唯有親自下去找找看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.15,0:12:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等，如果需要的話我和部下去便足夠了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.79,0:12:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你願意幫我忙？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.99,0:12:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我當然願意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.07,0:12:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是你部下啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.69,0:12:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然現在是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.95,0:13:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但本來你是我二哥的部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.73,0:13:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.33,0:13:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看你比平時緊張得多呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.03,0:13:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別要因為女孩子而急於立功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.70,0:13:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要鎮定！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.70,0:13:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你全權處理吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.87,0:13:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟說我為了依榭蓮娜而急於立功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.51,0:13:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒可能...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.81,0:13:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是相當冷靜的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.35,0:13:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.42,0:13:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現他們要立即通知我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.42,0:13:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待我打敗他們給你看！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.19,0:13:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要你專誠來送我真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.13,0:13:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也有這個打算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.99,0:13:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託了，卡爾瑪上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.53,0:13:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託了，夏亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.20,0:13:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝利的榮耀是屬於你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.18,0:14:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長，有3台機動戰士下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還正向我們這邊來呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.72,0:14:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的！阿姆羅，聽到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.98,0:14:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZAKU來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.76,0:14:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快讓GUNDAM出去應戰吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.94,0:14:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.33,0:14:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用剛才你說的戰術去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.50,0:14:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去引開ZAKU
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.47,0:14:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最好把敵人本隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.70,0:14:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以引他們來母艦的前方嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.91,0:14:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後由母艦作主力攻擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.47,0:14:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.44,0:14:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼坦克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.38,0:14:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼加農準備待命出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.18,0:14:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.52,0:14:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先去那邊看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.13,0:15:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得利用自己人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.08,0:15:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是太好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.77,0:15:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木馬那邊好像有機動戰士來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.51,0:15:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被發現了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.62,0:15:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.49,0:15:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.17,0:15:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人在附近！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.84,0:15:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.35,0:16:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是夏亞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.73,0:16:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停下來會危險！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.00,0:16:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機動戰士的動作愈來愈靈活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.96,0:16:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一手呢，機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.99,0:16:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他似乎想叫我到別的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.13,0:17:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亦即是說，木馬在後面？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.64,0:17:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們真想得周到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.00,0:17:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要報這個仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.74,0:17:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我等你很久了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.44,0:17:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機動戰士想逃走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.04,0:17:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母艦應在前面，追著它！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.81,0:17:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.00,0:17:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開激光炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.70,0:17:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部準備開火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.27,0:17:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長，敵軍向前飛去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.34,0:17:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，米萊，回崗位吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.18,0:17:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要開始攻擊了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.13,0:17:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.16,0:18:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼坦克，鋼加農
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.81,0:18:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,及母艦內各炮位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.43,0:18:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡烏無防備背向著我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.63,0:18:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十秒後開始發射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.20,0:18:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,10...9...8...7...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.07,0:18:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,6...5...4...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.68,0:18:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,3...2...1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.01,0:18:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.61,0:18:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼會這樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.98,0:18:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有敵機在後面攻擊我們！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.68,0:18:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後面？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.28,0:18:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是木馬！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.36,0:18:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木馬在後面！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.62,0:18:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上升！上升啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.28,0:18:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.82,0:19:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,180度回轉吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.96,0:19:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要和木馬同歸於盡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.64,0:19:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡爾瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.31,0:19:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就去詛咒你天生的不幸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.51,0:19:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？天生的不幸？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.18,0:19:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對，不幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.68,0:19:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞！原來你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.55,0:19:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然你是個好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.56,0:19:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但卻是你父親不好啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.16,0:19:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏...夏亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.52,0:19:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你暗算我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.89,0:19:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.14,0:19:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別小看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.89,0:19:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是薩比家的男子漢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.54,0:19:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是不會白白送死的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.15,0:20:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵軍卡烏正面飛過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.38,0:20:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.58,0:20:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道是敢死隊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.52,0:20:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊，快向上升，向上升！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.86,0:20:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緊急向上升！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.74,0:20:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全體人員伏下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.94,0:20:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION公國榮耀長在！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.68,0:21:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...我們得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.78,0:21:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，你做得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.70,0:21:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突破作戰成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.49,0:21:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在立即離開這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.95,0:21:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.83,0:21:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，你做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.21,0:21:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.16,0:21:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道...我立即回來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.98,0:21:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎，我明白了，謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.77,0:21:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會告訴她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.49,0:21:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依榭蓮娜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.69,0:21:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.82,0:21:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依榭蓮娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.07,0:21:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說卡爾瑪在戰場戰死了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.25,0:22:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡爾瑪少爺...你怎可以死？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.79,0:22:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡爾瑪少爺...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.19,0:22:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡爾瑪少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.46,0:22:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個自稱為ZION的宇宙都市國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.20,0:22:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是在月球的另一邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.00,0:22:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們的領袖現在所得到\N卡爾瑪戰死的壞消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.69,0:22:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION公國的國王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.65,0:23:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亦是卡爾瑪的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.17,0:23:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪金薩比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.87,0:23:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收到噩耗後整個人呆了\N令牌也在使者面前掉落...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.76,0:23:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥沒有結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.84,0:23:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了替卡爾瑪報仇，殘存部隊發動了特攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.01,0:23:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和良的鋼加農一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.98,0:23:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻擊卡烏的阿姆羅面前站著一位美少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.08,0:23:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顫抖的手槍對著阿姆羅……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.08,0:23:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機動戰士GUNDAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.71,0:23:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一集 『伊榭蓮娜的悲戀』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.35,0:23:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能夠存活下去嗎？

